   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Bolanus, strategos of the Arsinoite nome, Themistos [and Polemon divisions], from Chairemon, village secretary [of - - -. Being asked you to submit names (of persons)] for the supervision of dykes (chomatekbolia) [and for - - -] of the canals of the present [. . year - - -]</ab>
         </div>
         <div type="bibliography" subtype="citations">
